Top Strategy Analysis

Primary Strategy

Video Tutorials &
"Behind the Scenes"

Why it works (Pros)

"Visually demonstrates expertise while building a high-engagement SEO pipeline and reusable assets."

Considerations (Cons)

High production costs and time investment; requires consistent output to gain initial traction.

Implementation Roadmap

  • 1

    Keyword & Planning

    Map out 3-5 core tutorials based on client pain points.

  • 2

    Production Setup

    Invest in quality audio/video gear or audit outsourcing options.

  • 3

    Launch & Synergize

    Deploy on YouTube/Blog and cross-promote via all channels.

Next Action Steps

  • 1

    Define Theme

    Set rules for the first "Design Challenge" & Live slot.

  • 2

    Hype Campaign

    Use countdowns and reels to drive live attendance.

  • 3

    Moderate & Engage

    Prepare talking points and manage live submissions.
